{"tid":936941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【卵子質素差】蒼井空克服不育 拖老公宣佈懷孕五個月","createTime":"2018-12-11T07:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T07:32:48.000Z","uid":48093,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"510d7ced83c402dcad9dd0c45a3509da9170224c","tid":936941,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181211/large/1544511406_499e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181211%2Flarge%2F1544511406_499e.jpg&h=e503271b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年35歲嘅日本前AV女優蒼井空今年元旦宣佈閃婚，與其貌不揚嘅DJ NON拉埋天窗，蒼老師在閃婚後多次透露希望可以生小朋友，仲一度發福傳出懷孕消息。今日，蒼井空在台灣舉行記者會，仲同老公DJ NON齊齊現身，宣佈造人成功陀B五個月。蒼老師表示：「我很激動，也很感恩，希望我的寶寶能感受到大家的祝福，一路以來我是個幸福的人，也希望繼續努力堅持做自己，謝謝大家！」<br />\n蒼老師婚後曾在網誌上承認有造人計劃，無奈發現自己嘅卵子發育不佳，導致未能順利懷孕，並有接受治療，如今終於克服不孕，明年將榮升媽咪達成心願。"},{"pid":"7880717e2533ffa5e1b25127afc07ed413a560cc","tid":936941,"uid":105678,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:20:55.000Z","msg":"大個個仔可以J翻老母後生啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3865d66f17a4f934d25f819fa518c03b291d1c","tid":936941,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:26:12.000Z","msg":"選排卵期幾天，招待成班男優開p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點弱都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa680596ac26e4c3f15fb8bfc6b7ab4cddb71f0","tid":936941,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7880717e2533ffa5e1b25127afc07ed413a560cc","tid":936941,"uid":105678,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:20:55.000Z","msg":"大個個仔可以J翻老母後生啲片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"佢生仔真係有冇諗過仔女大個咗會點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非佢而家